title: VA: Metal Rock - Fix Me (Dutch Treat ^A171 HQ VBR MP3)
description:
A meditation on my own request:
Sometimes you need to be really depressed, just to know what Music does to you.
Well fortunately that is not very hard in this world.
Did the MAD project (Music Against Depression) once. But this time, I need something stronger.
So let's Rock; Cheer me Up....scotty (It won't be easy).

And so it was. Not easy. So I switched to Metal and Gothic to find my way out there.
The Sound may be a bit dark colored (like I am now) but somehow fits the being-in-a-save-cellar experience.
Hereby 15 tracks of the ones that came close. One hour of Metal (and nice) Moments..... Enjoy,
